<MELItem itemNbr="23-51-06" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-23-51-06.1.2-23-51-06">
<Title>Audio Gateway Units</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="4" nbrRequired="3" opsIndicator="(O)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>Forward right audio gateway unit may be inoperative provided:</Para>
<List listType="a.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Service interphone nose gear jack is considered inoperative.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Operations procedure is used.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Note>
<Para>The airplane must also be dispatched using MEL item 23-41-01-01.</Para>
</Note>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceNote>
<Para>The audio gateway units are interchangeable.</Para>
</MaintenanceNote>
<OperationProcedure>
<Para>Audio identification will not be available for the following:  ILS-R, GLS-R, VOR-R, DME-R.  Use the PFD/ND to verify tuning of the associated receiver.</Para>
</OperationProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
